Interface Alyx

        AlyxStorageEngine getStorageEngine()

      • loadPlugin

        void loadPlugin​(AlyxPlugin<?> plugin)
         throws AlyxException
        Loads the specified plugin into this instance of Alyx.
        Parameters:
        plugin - The plugin to load.
        Throws:
        AlyxException - Exception thrown if the plugin is not registered.

      • unloadPlugin

        void unloadPlugin​(AlyxPlugin<?> plugin)
           throws AlyxException
        Unloads the specified plugin from this instance of Alyx. If the plugin is guarded, an AlyxException will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        plugin - The plugin to unload.
        Throws:
        AlyxException - Exception thrown if unloading the plugin fails (it is not registered or is guarded).

      • registerParameterParser

        void registerParameterParser​(ParameterParser<?> parser)
        Registers a ParameterParser for use in Alyx when parsing command strings. TODO: This should happen as part of the plugin registration process. Make them specific to plugins so that each plugin can handle same types differently?
        Parameters:
        parser - The parser to register. This will (currently) override any other existing parsers for the parser's type.
